adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如上面兩條片下面個個都有介紹過佢錄音都要經interface插電腦錄，咁條cover片應該點整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d1605271dd1e395883a5552c3039216ef2722e","tid":290801,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"試下search youtube<br />\n<br />\nmic setup for youtube<br />\nmic aetup for singing<br />\n<br />\n之類"},{"pid":"03ffd15db37715e7d03311e38b1adeb7db86c129","tid":290801,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下search youtube<br />\n<br />\nmic setup for youtube<br />\nmic aetup for singing<br />\n<br />\n之類</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我search search先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343eea4922db29c2329990c0587c970fa22c15ed","tid":290801,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你用咩錄影&hellip;iphone?相機？<br />\n<br />\n用個外置mic試下先</blockquote><br />\n有個rode USB 咪直插電腦，因為玩開音樂，係GarageBand 錄音多<br />\n<br />\n但如果cover想拍埋片，想用枝usb咪收音自彈自唱，但枝咪好似只可以<span style=\"color: red;\">直插</span>電腦錄音，如果例如想用iphone拍片之後用枝咪收音，應該後期係剪片程式度將條片同條聲同步番？<br />\n<br />\n定應該點做可以方便d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如上面兩條片下面個個都有介紹過佢錄音都要經interface插電腦錄，咁條cover片應該點整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"594e0bfc7d36253448c1c4f0d3c8a4b0bb373838","tid":2908